The Silhouette America® website provides the ability to purchase products, both physical and digital. You are able to add products to your cart that you wish to order by clicking on the “Add to Cart” button located on the product details page. Placing an item in your shopping cart does not reserve the item. Products are reserved only upon successfully completing the checkout process. Successfully completed orders will receive an automated email confirming order placement.
All orders are final once you have completed the checkout process and paid for the order. Orders cannot be altered to have items added, removed, or individually canceled once the order has been placed. If you wish to cancel an order, you must contact Silhouette Support within 24 hours of order placement. Cancellation requests may take up to 48 hours to complete. Requests to cancel do not guarantee successful cancellation. In the case your order has shipped prior to successful cancellation, it is your responsibility to refuse the delivery or return the order per the
Product Return Policy
