18. Pricing
All product pricing listed on this website is in US Dollars (USD). Product prices listed on this website are subject to change without notice. All pricing listed at the moment of purchase is the applicable price that will be charged, except in the case where pricing information on the website may contain an error. Silhouette America® is not bound by offers listed in error and reserves the right to make corrections for any such errors and/or cancel orders where there have been errors in pricing.
Sales tax is not included in the listed price of any download content. Sales tax is assessed based on your zip or postal code for orders placed within select areas in the United States, and will be applied per applicable sales tax law where required. You can view the presence of sales tax and sales tax information prior to check-out while viewing your Shopping Cart.
Silhouette America® does not offer price matching on products purchased from other websites or store locations, or for shipping costs offered from other websites.
19. Shipping
Orders placed on
www.silhouetteamerica.com
can only be shipped within the United States, Canada, and US Territories (Guam, Northern Mariana Islands, Puerto Rico, and Virgin Islands). Canadian shipments are subject to import duties, taxes, and/or customs fees which are imposed by the local government once the package is received. You are solely responsible for any such fees.
Silhouette America® does not ship to hotels or other temporary locations. Any returned orders resulting from shipping to temporary locations will result in a restocking fee of up to 20%.
Shipping rates are based on the weight of products being purchased along with your zip or postal code (US only), or other allowable shipping area location. You can get an estimated shipping cost prior to check-out while viewing your Shopping Cart. Exact shipping cost is calculated on the final checkout page prior to placing the order. Silhouette America® cannot be held responsible for discrepancies between estimated shipping costs displayed in the shopping cart page and the actual shipping costs displayed during final check out. By proceeding to place your order, you confirm that you understand that your order may be split between more than one Silhouette fulfillment center dependent upon product availability and you consent to be charged additional shipping costs associated with such multiple shipments, when applicable.
Allow 7 - 12 days for delivery of any order placed through
www.silhouetteamerica.com
. Silhouette America® cannot guarantee delivery by a specific date. Actual ship times are dependent upon the delivery service of the shipping carrier being used and may be affected or increased during promotional periods. Silhouette America® does not offer expedited shipping options. An automated email with tracking information will be issued to your Silhouette account email address once your order is shipped. You may also sign into your Silhouette account and click on the “my account” link. From here you may view any recent order and tracking information (present if your order has been shipped).
Silhouette America® cannot adjust your shipping address once the order is delivered to the carrier. You are solely responsible for the risk of loss for products purchased through
www.silhouetteamerica.com
once they are delivered to the carrier.
