Silhouette hardware warranty information
for Silhouette Products
Limited Warranty
Silhouette America, Inc. offers a limited one-year warranty on its machines. If, at any time during the first year from the date of purchase, a Silhouette support representative cannot resolve a concern through troubleshooting or diagnosis, Silhouette America® will repair or replace the machine (at its option). Silhouette America warrants that the machine, when used in accordance with all manufacturer's instructions, will perform substantially in accordance with the accompanying documentation for its intended use during the warranty period. Silhouette America does not warrant that the machine will perform without interruption or error or that the software will be completely free of bugs. Silhouette America does not warrant consumable machine replacement parts, such as blades and cutting mats.
Who Makes This Warranty
The warranty is made by Silhouette America, Inc., 600 North 2000 West, Lindon, UT 84042.
Who is Covered
This warranty extends only to the original purchaser of the product as purchased through an authorized Silhouette dealer. This warranty is intended for natural persons only and does not extend to any corporation, limited-liability company, or commercial entity.
What is Covered
This warranty covers manufacturing defects only. It includes parts and labor and the cost of shipping the repaired (or replaced) product from Silhouette America to you. The cost of shipping the product to Silhouette America for evaluation is not covered.
Replacement of Machine Parts
If Silhouette America elects to replace a defective machine, or any part thereof, the original machine becomes Silhouette America's property. Silhouette America may replace the entire machine or any defective component thereof, at its option. After full evaluation of the returned machine by our warranty department, if a manufacturer's defect is confirmed, a new replacement unit will be issued, dependent upon inventory. If a manufacturer's defect cannot be confirmed, a refurbished (like-new) unit may be issued, dependent upon inventory.
All refurbished units receive a full inspection to ensure proper working condition, appearance, and quality. All refurbished units come with a 30-day limited warranty to cover any defects that may arise during that time frame. In all approved warranty cases, a like model will be issued. Silhouette America cannot substitute alternate machine models or issue monetary reimbursement or other forms of compensation.
Replacement of Limited Edition Products
Limited edition products, including alternate product color variants, are covered under warranty as stated in the "Limited Warranty" section above. However, limited edition products, including color variants, may not be able to be replaced with an identical unit. After full evaluation of the returned unit by our warranty department, if a manufacturer's defect is confirmed, a new replacement unit of like or similar product variation will be issued, dependent upon available inventory. If inventory of a like or similar product variant is unavailable, Silhouette America shall issue a new, available, standard, nonexclusive unit. If a manufacturer's defect cannot be confirmed, a refurbished (like-new) unit of like or similar product variation will be issued, dependent upon available inventory. If inventory of like or similar product variant is unavailable, Silhouette America shall issue an available, standard, nonexclusive, refurbished (like-new) unit.
A repair option may be offered as an alternative for limited edition (color variation) units.
Where and How to Obtain Warranty Service
United States and Canadian customers can obtain warranty service from Silhouette America at the following address. It is your responsibility to contact Silhouette America to obtain a return authorization number and then deliver or ship the defective product to us at your expense, together with a copy of your receipt showing date of purchase and a description of the claimed defect, prior to the expiration of the warranty period.
Silhouette America may accept a written affirmation of purchase in lieu of a purchase receipt in appropriate circumstances. Silhouette America will not accept unsolicited returns without accompany of a return authorization number. To obtain information regarding this warranty, you may contact us by mail, email, or online:
